{"tid":2329860,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知Ram問題定係老母板問題","createTime":"2020-12-17T13:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T01:54:05.000Z","uid":306444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b50ce8bef6cd1d27a83e05df86757438f07bd1ff","tid":2329860,"uid":306444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"老母板 ROG Z390-E<br />\nRam Corsair 4x16GB 3200<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前一直開心使用四條<br />\n後尾就開唔到機 用返兩條(A) 插1.3位着到機<br />\n但係插埋另外兩條(B) 2.4位就黑mon冇畫面<br />\n<br />\n用(A)試 2.4位開唔到機<br />\n用(B)試1.3位開唔到機<br />\n剩係得用(A)插1.3位正常使用<br />\n<br />\n究竟係咪兩樣都有問題<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c689e16de4d826a04b4dea4cd41f741be27ed108","tid":2329860,"uid":306444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"牛 RM750"},{"pid":"9cdde112cf3513af494bbb547d1f033187d35a1d","tid":2329860,"uid":303571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"搵人check B個對ram應該最多<br />\n但你到最後點都係要兩個Check哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e936b1ba6236a88d9818c12db91501b8e4a2a73","tid":2329860,"uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"我都試過最後發現 係Cpu針彎咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a278097b2fa6802fbb72804aadc84198084a07","tid":2329860,"uid":303571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cdde112cf3513af494bbb547d1f033187d35a1d","tid":2329860,"uid":303571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"搵人check B個對ram應該最多<br />\n但你到最後點都係要兩個Check哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"*最快"},{"pid":"0ccc36ba7aa38a18a8df0f56a4a36deb1059ffce","tid":2329860,"uid":335003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e936b1ba6236a88d